Pester has to jump through a lot of hoops to be able to do what it does. There are few tricks regarding scopes that you most likely don't know and that I find very interesting. 

> The title is obviously a tribute to [Kevin Marquette's](https://powershellexplained.com/) series explaining, hashtables, arrays, null and so on.



